pulses.name: 20250219 Most Active Threat Indicators
pulses.description:
19 Feb 2025 : Most Active Threat Indicators
#Cybersecurity #Cyberattack #RCE #Botnet #IOC

Top 3 Source Countries:
- United States (US): Demonstrates diverse cyber activity, including SystemBC botnet operations, back orifice traffic, ZGrab scanning, and general HTTP exploits. Note that the US is both a prime target and a major source of cyberattacks.
- China (CN): Involved in a variety of attacks, including those targeting D-Link devices, NETGEAR DGN1000, Zivif web cameras, and various botnet activities. China has been identified as a major player in cyber espionage.
- India (IN): Shows activity related to D-Link devices, Dasan GPON, NETGEAR DGN1000, and multiple router exploits.
